Shape matters in protein mobility within membranes

François Quemeneura,b,c,d, Jon K. Sigurdssone, Marianne Rennerf,g, Paul J. Atzbergere,1, Patricia Bassereaua,b,c,d,1, and David Lacosted,h,i,1,2
